# LF everywhere, regardless of a contributor's local core.autocrlf setting
# or OS — this repo standardizes on LF (matches Biome's default lineEnding).
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never text-normalize these.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
